# SharpInvoice Technology Stack

This rule outlines the key technologies and libraries for the backend.

- **Framework**: [ASP.NET Core](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/apps/aspnet)
- **Database ORM**: [Entity Framework Core](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/ef/core/) with SQL Server.
- **Authentication**: Custom JWT-based system.
- **Password Hashing**: [BCrypt.Net](https://github.com/BcryptNet/bcrypt.net).
- **External Logins**: OAuth 2.0 for Google and Facebook.
- **PDF Generation**: [QuestPDF](https://www.questpdf.com/).
- **Email**: [SendGrid](https://sendgrid.com/) is used for sending emails.

